unning in a day, using the EnableHTML, the built-in AuthUser, HtpasswdForm, NewpageBox+, Discussion Tab, SectionEdit, and the Monobook recipes, we were able to replicate 99.9%25 of the ''other'' wiki software's functionality that our authors came to expect.  The other 0.1%25 of functionality will probably pop up and slap me in the face, because I'm sure it's already there; I just haven't found it yet.%0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a%0a----%0a%0a%25lfloat%25 [[Attach:PassageSite.jpg -> http://www.thepassageride.com]]%0a!!!![[http://www.thepassageride.com | The Passage of a Few People Through a Rather Brief Moment in Time]]%0a%0aOne or more persons during a certain period drop their usual motives for movement and action, their relations, their work and leisure activities, and let themselves be drawn by the attractions of the terrain and the encounters they find there.%0a%0aIt’s a bike ride. It happens weekly, in Los Angeles.%0a%0aThis is its website: [[http://www.thepassageride.com | thepassageride.com]] %0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a%0a----%25lfloat margin-right:10px%25  [[http://paulellisproducer.com/ | http://eclectichosting.net/portfolio/paulellisproducer.com-thumb.jpg]]%0a%0a(:table margin-left=10px border=1 width=30%25 align=right bgcolor=#ccffff cellspacing=0 :)%0a(:cellnr:)%0a'''[[http://eclectictech.net/ | Eclectic Tech site]]'''\\%0a[[~XES | by The Crisses]]%0a(:cellnr:)%0a*Video content%0a*Audio content%0a*Google Maps%0a*Calendar of events%0a*Dynamic content features%0a(:tableend:)%0a%0a!!![[http://paulellisproducer.com/ | PEP Productions, Chester & Sugar Loaf, NY]]%0aPaul Ellis can control the text at the upper right corner of the page by entering wiki [=(:data:)=] information on the page -- so he could have a different saying on every page if he wanted to.  This company produces live plays, radio plays, events, and just about anything that has more than one person in a room -- but his specialty is arts and theatre.%0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a----%0a%25lfloat margin-right:10px%25  [[http://persona